headline.print_headline: Program That Accepted Rice Rare in Domestic Cases
headline.main: Program That Accepted Rice Rare in Domestic Cases

lead_paragraph: The offender-rehabilitation program former Baltimore Raven Ray Rice was allowed into after knocking his fiancee unconscious in an Atlantic City elevator is rarely used in domestic assault cases — but whether that means he got special treatment because of his stardom remains up in the air, depending on whom you ask.
